long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Ready to dive into a world of challenging puzzles and hilarious trolling moments? The Level Devil - Troll Game Chrome extension brings you brain-teasing levels designed to test your logic and sense of humor! ğŸ®ğŸ§©

What does it do?
This extension allows you to play Level Devil right from your browser! It offers a series of clever puzzles that seem simple at first, but each level hides a tricky troll twist. You'll need to think outside the box, expect the unexpected, and use your creativity to solve each challenge.

Why install it?

Fun and engaging: Perfect for a quick break or long play sessions!
No downloads needed: Play directly from your browser, hassle-free.
Challenging puzzles: Test your logic and patience with levels that constantly surprise you.
Troll humor: Laugh out loud as the game tricks you with clever twists and turns.
Plus, enjoy seamless gameplay with a top-left menu for easy navigation and icons to rate, share, and go fullscreen at the bottom-right. Ready to get trolled? Install Level Devil and let the fun begin! ğŸ˜ˆâœ¨
